name: Whisper of Yesterday
description:
Maybe show her some understanding. Give her time, let her breathe, let her live.
Interactive OBJKT. 
How to? Click/Tap anywhere to start the journey. Click "Play" to enable the music and "Mute" to disable. Click "Restart" to start the journey from the beginning.
Interact with the desktop to get the best experience. Hover or click around the particle.
